{"blogid": "123913216", "writerAge": "码龄5年", "writerBlogNum": "57", "writerCollect": "27", "writerComment": "2", "writerFan": "96", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "670", "writerName": "编程经验随笔", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_123913216.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "28494", "writerRankWeekly": "26208", "writerThumb": "9", "writerVisitNum": "32768", "blog_read_count": "1593", "blog_time": "已于 2022-04-02 15:14:10 修改", "blog_title": "CString头文件怎么用？", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p>在非MFC工程中.就包含atlstr.h</p>\n<p>在MFC工程中.就包含afx.h</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>一般我们会使用MFC in ShareDLL的方式</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"526\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0bc56de964d54f9582af75c6f48ef4db.png\" width=\"767\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>然后需要包含stdafx.h 避免一些编译错误</p>\n<p>stdafx.h的内容如下</p>\n<p>#pragma once</p>\n<p>#ifdef _DEBUG<br/> #define _AFXDLL<br/> #endif<br/> #include &lt;afxwin.h&gt;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>在代码中正常使用 CString 就可以了 不需要ATL::CString去引用，也没有二义性的问题</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>注意：#include \"stdafx.h\"要放在引用的cpp文件的最上面</p>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Others", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-04-02 15:14:10", "summary": "在非工程中就包含在工程中就包含一般我们会使用的方式然后需要包含避免一些编译错误的内容如下在代码中正常使用就可以了不需要去引用，也没有二义性的问题注意：要放在引用的文件的最上面"}